{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"69d49b2122","title":"复彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"28d73cc71a","index":0,"year":1949,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"69d49b2122"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"f63599462b","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"69d49b2122","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"9月2日毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致彭德怀、张宗逊电，询问是否可于9月15日以前占领青海、宁夏。3日，彭、张复电说：15日占西宁有可能，9月底能占宁夏省会。这是毛泽东复彭德怀并告贺龙、习仲勋电的主要内容。"},{"id":"5ea654ed3b","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"69d49b2122","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"马鸿宾，当时任国民党西北军政长官公署副长官。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5e70bb50d1","type":"title","text":"复彭德怀电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"69d49b2122"},{"id":"f63599462b","type":"paragraph","text":"向青、宁进军以适合情况解决问题，不使军队太疲劳为原则，早一点退一点都可以。宁夏马军力争全部缴械，其次则争取大部缴械，一部改编。总之，改编的部队意少意好。请考虑利用马鸿宾，派人向马鸿宾做些工作，争取大部和平缴械，一部改编的局面。宁夏人少地狭，马部军政党可能有二十万人，加上十九兵团十万人，粮食问题必甚严重，请预为筹备。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"69d49b2122"}],"page":{"id":"7eeef65916","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"69d49b2122","start":206,"end":206}}}},"__N_SSG":true}